    <div class="container pt-17 pb-15 py-sm-17">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-xxl-5 text-center text-sm-start" data-cues="slideInDown" data-group="page-title" data-interval="-200" data-delay="500">
          <h2 class="display-1 fs-56 mb-4 ls-xs pe-xl-5 pe-xxl-0">Let Tucson's junk removal <span class="underline-3 style-3 yellow">specialists</span> make you happy.</h2>
          <p class="lead fs-23 lh-sm mb-7 pe-lg-5 pe-xl-5 pe-xxl-0">From appliance pickup and furniture removal all the way to whole house and warehouse cleanouts, we got you covered.</p>
