            <h2 class="display-3 mb-3">Our process couldn't be easier</h2>
            <p class="lead fs-lg mb-6">If we made it any simpler, it would literally be magic.</p>
            <div class="d-flex flex-row mb-6">
                <div>
                <span class="icon btn btn-circle btn-outline-primary pe-none me-5"><span class="number fs-18">1</span></span>
                </div>
